Kirsten Cooke https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kirsten_Cooke 0 Kirsten Cooke (born 4 October 1952, in Cuckfield, West Sussex, England) is an English stage actress who trained at the Webber Douglas Academy of Dramatic Art, London. Almost all of her acting work has been in comedy.
